snippet.title: AMAZING: Johnny Depp THANKS his SUPPORTERS for defending him against Amber Heard (Video)
snippet.description:
With everything going on at the moment between Johnny and Amber, Johnny Depp thanks his supporters for defending him against Amber Heard. 
In a public statement he thanked his fans for sticking with him on a long road. He really needs some people to stand up for him, since it's been a rough time. Who better to sax thank you to, than his loyal fans?
